Exploration enrichment pathways with differentially expressed (DE) genes between old versus young

Team Le Grand

02 mai,2022

Pathway explored : REACTOME RECOGNITION AND ASSOCIATION OF DNA GLYCOSYLASE WITH SITE CONTAINING AN AFFECTED PURINE

This pathway contain 50 genes.

In these 50 genes for each day and cell type, they are not all expressed and they are not all differentially expressed between old versus young.

Inside these differents genes, there are (cf table below) number of genes DE significant with a major participation in the enrichment (leadingEdge cal by fgsea filter by padj<0.05).
